. And once again, please don't take this wrong, but I was/am bored with my druid. And likewise mages out there, I'm not asking for you to get a nerfing! You ARE the masters of summoning, and I can see why your pets should be the beasts they are. We are what we are, all of us. That what I was trying to get across in my last post, which apparently people didn't like. Oh well. We all have strengths and weaknesses...although I can't think of one for a druid off the top of my head!  j/k  =P  And I also play a mage on Fennin Ro. Ok, not anywhere close to being high lvl with him, but I'm there at least. It just gets old, nerf the necro nerf the necro...almost makes me wish we still had Abashi! Ok, maybe not...  Just play your class, and if you don't like what another can do, deal with it. Or play that class instead.<br><br>Karkas 49 DE Why-can't-we-just-get-along-Necro<br>Quellious<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
